    An abstract representation of a region. Venue acts as a physical location and allows us to group Device objects together. Additionally it's a describable container for devices which can be signified with image cover. A venue belongs to the Manager that created it and can be shared to the other ones by his owner.
    We can obtain venues via IKontaktCloud.
